Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.85,0:02:41.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイト。\Nうっ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.07,0:02:39.87,phi main,,0,0,0,,Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.19,0:02:44.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きのうのルーク君のこと？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.42,0:02:43.32,phi main,,0,0,0,,Are you still thinking about what Rook said yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:54.07,phi main,,0,0,0,,I'll come again. Wait for me, Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.60,0:02:55.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,回想\Nまた来るよ。　待っててね　カイト。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.85,0:03:03.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪い。　少し　１人にしてくれ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.15,0:03:01.86,phi main,,0,0,0,,Sorry, could you leave me alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.56,0:03:12.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ソウジ）カイト君が見たという\N滅亡の未来…　本当に来るのかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.72,0:03:12.79,phi main,,0,0,0,,Will that apocalyptic future that Kaito saw really come?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.57,0:03:16.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（キュービック）現在のデータを基に\N導き出された答えにすぎない。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.79,0:03:16.77,phi main,,0,0,0,,It's merely a conclusion formed from the current data.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.59,0:03:20.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,条件が変われば　その答えも\N変わるはずだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.77,0:03:20.28,phi main,,0,0,0,,If the variables change, the result will change too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.19,0:03:25.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それより　ルーク・盤城・クロスフィールドも\Nファイ・ブレインの子供だったとはね。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.28,0:03:25.86,phi main,,0,0,0,,But more importantly, Rook Banjo Crossfield is a child of the Phi Brain too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.68,0:03:33.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかもカイトと違って　オルペウスの腕輪が\N常に発動した状態でいるようだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.86,0:03:31.95,phi main,,0,0,0,,And unlike Kaito, his Armband seems to be active already.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.36,0:03:38.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが　ファイ・ブレインとしての\N完成形ということなのかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.63,0:03:38.00,phi main,,0,0,0,,Is that the final form of the Phi Brain?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.53,0:03:42.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも　人間の脳が　そんな負担に…。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.80,0:03:42.07,phi main,,0,0,0,,Can the human brain endure that much strain?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:04:01.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ビショップ）\Nルーク様。　ピタゴラス伯爵は　本当に\Nお亡くなりになっているのですか。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.69,0:04:01.40,phi main,,0,0,0,,Sir Rook. Has Count Pythagoras really passed away?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.28,0:04:03.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ　隠されていたのです？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.40,0:04:03.49,phi main,,0,0,0,,Why did you keep it secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.39,0:04:08.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,部下たちが　いえ　ＰＯＧ全体が\N混乱しております。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.49,0:04:07.10,phi main,,0,0,0,,Our subordinates — no, the entire POG — is in chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.29,0:04:13.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それに　真方ジン。　まさか　直接\N管理なさっていたとは…。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.43,0:04:12.35,phi main,,0,0,0,,And you watched over Makata Jin directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.35,0:04:15.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一体　どのような\Nお考えがあって…。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.62,0:04:15.37,phi main,,0,0,0,,What were you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.37,0:04:18.57,phi main,,0,0,0,,It's fine. Everything is going well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.86,0:04:21.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫。　全ては\Nうまくいっている…　ビショップ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:20.57,phi main,,0,0,0,,Bishop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:36.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（バロン）管理官の大切な宝物に\N触れてしまった罰ですかね。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:35.68,phi main,,0,0,0,,Is this the punishment for touching the Chief's treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.95,0:04:39.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ！　ギャモン君。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:39.38,phi main,,0,0,0,,Gammon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.32,0:04:42.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君には　おとがめは\Nなかったようですね。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.38,0:04:41.73,phi main,,0,0,0,,They didn't punish you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.29,0:04:45.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ギャモン）ルークの許可が下りた…\N殺し合いのな。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.38,0:04:44.64,phi main,,0,0,0,,I got permission from Rook...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.64,0:04:45.72,phi main,,0,0,0,,for a deathmatch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.75,0:05:12.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が　世界を滅ぼす。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.90,0:05:11.65,phi main,,0,0,0,,I will destroy the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:44.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あそこは…。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.22,0:05:43.25,phi main,,0,0,0,,Is that...
