Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.80,0:05:51.91,phi main,,0,0,0,,Wait, what am I doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.71,0:05:56.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だ？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.07,0:05:54.95,phi main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.78,0:06:00.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アナ）えっ？！　あっ　ホントだ　カイト！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.94,0:05:59.29,phi main,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:00.17,phi main,,0,0,0,,Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.17,0:06:02.00,phi main,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.22,0:06:05.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よっ　よお！　相変わらずだな。\N絵　描いてたのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:03.94,phi main,,0,0,0,,You haven't changed a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.94,0:06:05.74,phi main,,0,0,0,,Are you painting?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.62,0:06:09.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アナが思うに　悩んでる。\Nうっ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.74,0:06:08.37,phi main,,0,0,0,,I think... something's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.23,0:06:11.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,描いても描いても\Nこうなっちゃう。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.42,0:06:11.82,phi main,,0,0,0,,No matter how much I paint, it always ends up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.58,0:06:15.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんでだろう？\Nお前のことかよ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.82,0:06:13.13,phi main,,0,0,0,,I wonder why.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.13,0:06:14.62,phi main,,0,0,0,,Oh, you meant yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.26,0:06:26.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お　お前…。　なんで　これを？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.42,0:06:26.21,phi main,,0,0,0,,H-How do you know about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.06,0:06:29.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしても　この風景に\Nなっちゃうんだなぁ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.21,0:06:29.20,phi main,,0,0,0,,It always ends up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.36,0:06:41.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アナは　太陽の絵が\N描きたかったのに…。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.59,0:06:41.46,phi main,,0,0,0,,I wanted to paint the Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.76,0:06:43.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,太陽？\Nうん。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.91,0:06:42.91,phi main,,0,0,0,,The Sun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.91,0:06:46.03,phi main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. So that even if the Sun goes far away,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.78,0:06:48.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,太陽が遠くに行っちゃったから\Nみんなを照らせるようにって。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.03,0:06:48.26,phi main,,0,0,0,,its light would remain here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.18,0:06:51.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも　遠くに行ってたのは\Nアナの方だから→
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:53.40,phi main,,0,0,0,,But I was the one who went far away, so I couldn't draw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.65,0:06:54.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,描けなかったんだね。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:02.28,phi main,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.66,0:07:03.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何するんだ？\N直すの。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.28,0:07:03.15,phi main,,0,0,0,,Fixing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:06.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,直す？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.89,0:07:05.02,phi main,,0,0,0,,Fixing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:10.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ。\N失敗したら直せばいい。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:10.78,phi main,,0,0,0,,If you fail, you should just fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.78,0:07:12.18,phi main,,0,0,0,,I should just fix it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.92,0:07:12.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,直せばいい…。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.96,0:07:16.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絵は　初めから\Nそこにあるわけじゃない。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.13,0:07:15.78,phi main,,0,0,0,,It's not like a painting is there from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.11,0:07:23.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いろんな色を混ぜて　塗り重ねて\N何度も何度も描き直して　描くの。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.25,0:07:22.29,phi main,,0,0,0,,You mix the colors, layer upon layer, and correct all the mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.08,0:07:26.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんなから　もらった思いを\N形にするの。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.64,0:07:26.75,phi main,,0,0,0,,You turn the feelings you got from others into a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:29.61,phi main,,0,0,0,,All the feelings, together with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.86,0:07:30.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんなの思いと　一緒に…。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.15,0:07:39.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,光は…　そこにある。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:39.08,phi main,,0,0,0,,The light is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.22,0:07:44.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絵を描くのが\N大好きな子がいました。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:44.11,phi main,,0,0,0,,There was a boy who loved to paint.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.86,0:07:48.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんな　「上手！　上手！」って\Nほめてくれましたけど→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.08,0:07:48.03,phi main,,0,0,0,,Everyone praised him for how good his pictures were,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.56,0:07:54.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その子には　ホントに描きたいものが\N分からなかったのです。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.71,0:07:52.73,phi main,,0,0,0,,but he didn't really know what he wanted to paint.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.38,0:07:58.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも　やっと出会えました。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.60,0:07:57.26,phi main,,0,0,0,,But then he found what he liked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.22,0:08:03.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,好きなもの\N本当に描きたいものに。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.38,0:08:01.98,phi main,,0,0,0,,What he really wanted to paint.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:08.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信じる太陽を…　光を…。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.70,0:08:07.24,phi main,,0,0,0,,The Sun he believed in... and its light.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:28.73,phi main,,0,0,0,,Thanks for bringing Kaito along.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.65,0:08:29.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがとう。\Nカイトを連れてきてくれて。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.36,0:08:43.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん。　今度は　うまく描けそう。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.57,0:08:42.11,phi main,,0,0,0,,I think it'll work out this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.55,0:08:52.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ。　お前？！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.43,0:08:51.28,phi main,,0,0,0,,You?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.42,0:08:54.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（エレナ）招待状をお持ちしました。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.65,0:08:54.76,phi main,,0,0,0,,I brought you an invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:09:00.07,phi main,,0,0,0,,The invitation to the last puzzle of Sakanoue Gammon, the Galileo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.91,0:09:01.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ガリレオ…　逆之上ギャモンの\N最後のパズルへの招待状です。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.98,0:09:36.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ルーク）約束どおり　迎えに来たよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.18,0:09:35.76,phi main,,0,0,0,,I promised I'd come for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.25,0:09:58.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイト…。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.46,0:09:57.18,phi main,,0,0,0,,Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.75,0:10:06.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（エレナ）これは　対戦型の支柱パズル。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:06.32,phi main,,0,0,0,,This is a beam duel puzzle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:12.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,先攻　後攻に分かれ　互いに番号を\Nコールすることで　パズルが進んでいく。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.92,0:10:11.97,phi main,,0,0,0,,Taking turns, the players call out numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.79,0:10:16.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,四方の壁からは　支柱が\N飛び出す仕掛けになっていて→
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.99,0:10:16.98,phi main,,0,0,0,,The beam of that number will come out from one of the four walls,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.78,0:10:21.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを効果的に使い\N先に地上へ出た者の勝ち。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.98,0:10:20.79,phi main,,0,0,0,,and whoever uses them better and gets to the surface first wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.61,0:10:25.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（エレナ）「先攻！　ガリレオ　逆之上ギャモン。→
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.92,0:10:25.02,phi main,,0,0,0,,First turn: Sakanoue Gammon, the Galileo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.48,0:10:29.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,後攻！　アインシュタイン　大門カイト。→
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.68,0:10:28.52,phi main,,0,0,0,,Second turn: Daimon Kaito, the Einstein.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:31.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,パズルタイム　スタート！」。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.38,0:10:31.11,phi main,,0,0,0,,Puzzle time, start!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.39,0:10:35.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見せてもらうわよ。→\N心の声
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.55,0:10:38.63,phi main,,0,0,0,,Show me your puzzle... the puzzle you made to betray your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.58,0:10:39.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんたが　仲間を\N心の声\N裏切ってまで作ったパズルを…。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.18,0:10:41.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ　始めるぜ！\Nうっ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.46,0:10:40.61,phi main,,0,0,0,,Let's start then!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.65,0:10:45.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,スペードの１００だ！\N（支柱が飛び出す音）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.72,0:10:43.28,phi main,,0,0,0,,Spades 100!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.24,0:10:52.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダイヤの９１！\N（支柱が飛び出す音）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.55,0:10:49.87,phi main,,0,0,0,,Diamonds 91!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.18,0:10:54.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（エレナ）いくつか　決まりがあるわ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.41,0:10:53.77,phi main,,0,0,0,,There are a few rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.56,0:10:58.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２人のプレーヤーは　同じ支柱に\N乗ってはいけない。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.77,0:10:57.99,phi main,,0,0,0,,The two players can't use the same beam.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.40,0:11:02.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おのおのが　自分のためだけに\N足場を造らなければいけない。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.58,0:11:02.08,phi main,,0,0,0,,They must build their own steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.69,0:11:06.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,支柱の数は\Nそれぞれの壁に１００ずつ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:06.31,phi main,,0,0,0,,There are a hundred beams in each wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:11.30,phi main,,0,0,0,,They can hit or even crush the opponent with the beams.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.49,0:11:11.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを相手にぶつけたり　支柱と\N支柱で　はさみつぶすことも可能。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.81,0:11:14.31,phi main,,0,0,0,,Clubs 86!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.18,0:11:15.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クラブの８６！\N（支柱が飛び出す音）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.42,0:11:19.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（２人）カイト！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.48,0:11:18.31,phi main,,0,0,0,,Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.76,0:11:27.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,野郎！　ハートの８５！\N（支柱が飛び出す音）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.91,0:11:22.87,phi main,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.87,0:11:24.67,phi main,,0,0,0,,Hearts 85!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.55,0:11:32.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,へっ！　スペードの９５！\N（支柱が飛び出す音）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.99,0:11:30.62,phi main,,0,0,0,,Spades 95!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:38.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（エレナ）その場合は　当然\N生き残ったプレーヤーの勝利。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.14,0:11:36.40,phi main,,0,0,0,,Or course, if that happens, the player alive wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.06,0:11:42.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっ。　ダイヤの８２。\N（支柱が飛び出す音）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.97,0:11:40.33,phi main,,0,0,0,,Diamonds 82!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.71,0:11:48.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２人とも生き残った場合でも\Nどちらかが先に地上へ上がると…。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.84,0:11:47.89,phi main,,0,0,0,,Even if they both stay alive, if one of them makes it to the surface...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:01.93,phi main,,0,0,0,,Clubs 77.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:04.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クラブの７７。\N（支柱が飛び出す音）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.87,0:12:06.62,phi main,,0,0,0,,Diamonds 73.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.98,0:12:08.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダイヤの７３！\N（支柱が飛び出す音）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.74,0:12:10.78,phi main,,0,0,0,,Clubs 68!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.82,0:12:11.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クラブの６８！\N（支柱が飛び出す音）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.72,0:12:14.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ！\Nやっぱり　こんなの　おかしいよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.41,0:12:14.37,phi main,,0,0,0,,This isn't normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.37,0:12:16.68,phi main,,0,0,0,,Why do Kaito and Gammon have to fight like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.48,0:12:19.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんで　カイトとギャモンが…！\Nやめさせて！　パズルを止めて！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.68,0:12:19.25,phi main,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Stop the puzzle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.01,0:12:22.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お願いだから。\N分かってるはずだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.25,0:12:20.80,phi main,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.80,0:12:22.19,phi main,,0,0,0,,You should understand already.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:27.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仲間じゃないか！\Nそれでも　ソルヴァーとギヴァーなんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.19,0:12:23.47,phi main,,0,0,0,,Aren't they friends?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.47,0:12:27.72,phi main,,0,0,0,,They are a Solver and a Giver.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.78,0:12:33.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイト…　ギャモン君…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.94,0:12:33.23,phi main,,0,0,0,,Kaito... Gammon...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.60,0:12:37.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうした？　カイト。　てめえの番だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.13,0:12:37.14,phi main,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Kaito? It's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.32,0:12:42.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（エレナ）アインシュタインの様子が　変ね。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.45,0:12:42.49,phi main,,0,0,0,,Einstein is acting weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.49,0:12:45.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ？\N支柱の選び方が単調すぎる。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.32,0:12:45.85,phi main,,0,0,0,,The way he's choosing the beams is too simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.57,0:12:50.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ガリレオを妨害しようとも　彼からの\N妨害を避けようともしない。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.85,0:12:50.38,phi main,,0,0,0,,He's not trying to obstruct Galileo or protect himself against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.13,0:12:53.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ単純に\N上を目指しているだけ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.38,0:12:53.30,phi main,,0,0,0,,He's just aiming for the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.11,0:12:56.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,キュービック君。\N思考速度は　通常のままだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.30,0:12:54.53,phi main,,0,0,0,,Cubic?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.53,0:12:57.08,phi main,,0,0,0,,His thinking is at normal speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.82,0:12:59.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,パズルに集中してないのかも。\Nそんな！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.08,0:12:59.00,phi main,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's not concentrating on the puzzle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.00,0:12:59.88,phi main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.88,0:13:04.27,phi main,,0,0,0,,I hope you're not thinking you can win without killing me, Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.92,0:13:04.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか　俺を殺さずに\N勝てると思ってんのか？　カイト！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:07.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かかってきやがれ！\Nいっ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.27,0:13:05.59,phi main,,0,0,0,,Come at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.08,0:13:14.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダイヤの…。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.22,0:13:12.31,phi main,,0,0,0,,Diamonds...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.29,0:13:17.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっ。\Nガリレオを傷つけるのを恐れて→
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.58,0:13:19.55,phi main,,0,0,0,,Is he holding back so that he won't hurt Galileo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.36,0:13:19.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手加減してるんじゃ\Nないでしょうね。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.41,0:13:22.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか　自分の脳に\N負担をかけまいとして。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.55,0:13:22.49,phi main,,0,0,0,,Or does he not want to strain his brain?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.81,0:13:25.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どちらも　ありえないよ。\N（２人）あっ？！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.30,0:13:24.80,phi main,,0,0,0,,Those are out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.81,0:13:30.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いったん　パズルを始めた以上　手を\N抜くようなマネは絶対にしない。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:30.45,phi main,,0,0,0,,Once you start a puzzle, there is no way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.62,0:13:33.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（キュービック）じゃあ　一体…。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:32.34,phi main,,0,0,0,,Then what...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.22,0:13:36.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪（ルーク）怖がることはない　カイト。\Nあっ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.36,0:13:35.58,phi main,,0,0,0,,Don't be afraid, Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.48,0:13:44.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ！　おいで。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.65,0:13:44.09,phi main,,0,0,0,,Come on up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.85,0:13:54.60,phi main,,0,0,0,,His thinking is speeding up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.99,0:13:54.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイトの思考が加速している！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.88,0:13:59.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダイヤの５４。\N（支柱が飛び出す音）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:13:58.10,phi main,,0,0,0,,Diamonds 54.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:02.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うわっ！　かっ　てん　うっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:06.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あぶね～　あぶね～。\Nやっと　面白くなってきたぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.96,0:14:04.57,phi main,,0,0,0,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:06.65,phi main,,0,0,0,,This is finally getting interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.92,0:14:10.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おめえの行く先は　読めてんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.08,0:14:09.45,phi main,,0,0,0,,I know where you're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.02,0:14:14.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クラブの５８。\N（支柱が飛び出す音）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.15,0:14:11.53,phi main,,0,0,0,,Clubs 58.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.51,0:14:17.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くそっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.58,0:14:19.32,phi main,,0,0,0,,Diamonds 45.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.72,0:14:23.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダイヤの４５。\N（支柱が飛び出す音）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.29,0:14:27.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,スペードの５４！\N（支柱が飛び出す音）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.46,0:14:24.81,phi main,,0,0,0,,Spades 54!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.49,0:14:31.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≫ダイヤの３６。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.71,0:14:29.25,phi main,,0,0,0,,Diamonds 36.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.98,0:14:33.18,phi main,,0,0,0,,Yes, just like that, Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.03,0:14:34.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それでいいんだ…　カイト。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.46,0:14:33.18,phi main,,0,0,0,,{gammon}Spades 44!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.78,0:14:40.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,思考速度が限界を超えた。\Nカイトの意識が　腕輪に取り込まれる。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.96,0:14:38.42,phi main,,0,0,0,,His thinking speed is beyond the limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.42,0:14:40.88,phi main,,0,0,0,,His mind has been taken over by the Armband!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.14,0:14:49.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハートの２４。\N（支柱が飛び出す音）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.43,0:14:47.72,phi main,,0,0,0,,Hearts 24.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.19,0:15:00.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,消えろ　お前…。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:10.30,phi main,,0,0,0,,They stopped moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:12.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,動きが止まった。\Nあと２手で　勝負は決まるわ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.30,0:15:12.18,phi main,,0,0,0,,In two moves, the fight will be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.12,0:15:15.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ？！\Nおそらく　カイト君の勝ちだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.09,0:15:15.35,phi main,,0,0,0,,And Kaito will probably win.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.94,0:15:18.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイト君が　あの支柱から\N動かないかぎり→
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.16,0:15:20.60,phi main,,0,0,0,,As long as Kaito doesn't move from that beam, Gammon can't go on upwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.63,0:15:20.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ギャモン君は　上に進めない。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.60,0:15:23.69,phi main,,0,0,0,,But if Kaito wins, Gammon will...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.68,0:15:24.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（キュービック）\Nでも…　カイトが勝ったら　ギャモンは…。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.55,0:15:32.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,スペードの１６。\N（支柱が飛び出す音）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.68,0:15:25.86,phi main,,0,0,0,,Spades 16.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.89,0:15:38.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やっぱ　動かねえか。\N心の声
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.01,0:15:38.36,phi main,,0,0,0,,He's not going to move?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:42.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,心の声\Nスペードの１６に上ったところを　たたき\N落としてやるつもりだったが…。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.36,0:15:42.21,phi main,,0,0,0,,I wanted to throw him off the moment he climbs spades 16.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.83,0:15:45.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ　お前の番だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.03,0:15:44.88,phi main,,0,0,0,,It's your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.38,0:15:53.34,phi main,,0,0,0,,If I use diamonds 18, Gammon will attack with a spades beam.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.51,0:15:53.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次に　ダイヤの１８を使えば\N心の声\Nギャモンは必ずスペードで攻撃してくる。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.19,0:15:57.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを　かわして\N心の声\Nその上に上れば…。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:55.97,phi main,,0,0,0,,I can dodge that and climb to the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.73,0:16:13.70,phi main,,0,0,0,,He'll be complete. He'll be complete soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.73,0:16:15.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,完成する…　もうすぐ完成する。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.18,0:16:19.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイト！　ギャモン君に勝たずに\Nパズルを解いて！\Nえっ？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.28,0:16:18.49,phi main,,0,0,0,,Kaito! Solve it without defeating Gammon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:23.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無理よ。　どちらかが　必ず死ぬ。\Nこのパズルは　そう出来てるの！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.17,0:16:22.27,phi main,,0,0,0,,It's impossible. One of them must die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.27,0:16:24.08,phi main,,0,0,0,,That's the point of this puzzle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.89,0:16:27.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それでも　なんとかしてくれる！\Nなんとかって？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.08,0:16:26.14,phi main,,0,0,0,,He'll do something about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.14,0:16:27.82,phi main,,0,0,0,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.63,0:16:32.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイトもギャモン君も　２人とも\N助かる方法があるかもしれない。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.82,0:16:31.01,phi main,,0,0,0,,There may be a way that both of them can get out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.08,0:16:35.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイトなら…　カイトなら　絶対…。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.23,0:16:35.51,phi main,,0,0,0,,Kaito... Kaito can find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.69,0:16:37.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうした？！　来い！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.90,0:16:37.98,phi main,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.76,0:16:40.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,パズルを…　パズルを解いて！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.98,0:16:40.84,phi main,,0,0,0,,Solve... Solve the puzzle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.73,0:16:44.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ルーク）そうだ…　そのまま進むんだ。\Nカイト。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.84,0:16:44.23,phi main,,0,0,0,,Go on, just like that, Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.91,0:16:48.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハ　ハートの…。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.06,0:16:48.27,phi main,,0,0,0,,Hearts...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.23,0:16:52.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや…　はっ？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:49.27,phi main,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.72,0:16:58.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,空想\N（ルーク）「捨てるんだ。\N友を…　感情を…」。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.84,0:16:57.53,phi main,,0,0,0,,Throw them away. Your friends. Your emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.14,0:17:05.29,phi main,,0,0,0,,Our future is waiting beyond.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.14,0:17:05.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,空想\N「その先に…　僕たちの未来が…」。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.88,0:17:24.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アナ）絵は　初めから\N回想\Nそこにあるわけじゃない。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.02,0:17:23.37,phi main,,0,0,0,,It's not like a painting is there from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.65,0:17:29.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,回想\Nいろんな色を混ぜて　塗り重ねて→
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:32.36,phi main,,0,0,0,,You mix the colors, layer upon layer, and correct all the mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.02,0:17:34.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,回想\N何度も何度も描き直して…\N描くの。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.01,0:17:37.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,回想　みんなから　もらった思いを\N形にするの。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.21,0:17:37.03,phi main,,0,0,0,,You turn the feelings you got from others into a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.52,0:17:40.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんなの思いと一緒に。\N回想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.67,0:17:39.42,phi main,,0,0,0,,All the feelings, together with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.18,0:17:42.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイト！\Nカイト！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:41.58,phi main,,0,0,0,,Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.58,0:17:42.95,phi main,,0,0,0,,Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.95,0:17:44.25,phi main,,0,0,0,,Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.95,0:17:44.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイト君！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:51.00,phi main,,0,0,0,,Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.51,0:17:50.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイト～～！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:17:58.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ。\N（２人）カイト！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.51,0:17:57.51,phi main,,0,0,0,,Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.93,0:18:12.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイト君…。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.13,0:18:11.48,phi main,,0,0,0,,Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.86,0:18:27.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はぁ！\Nカイト…。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.49,0:18:25.46,phi main,,0,0,0,,Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.88,0:18:30.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダイヤの７８！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:30.43,phi main,,0,0,0,,Diamonds 78!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.54,0:18:35.17,phi main,,0,0,0,,That idiot. That move is pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.59,0:18:35.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,野郎！　意味のねえ手を！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.51,0:18:39.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ギャモン）スペードの１４！\N（支柱が飛び出す音）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.64,0:18:36.98,phi main,,0,0,0,,Spades 14!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.58,0:18:43.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハートの１０。\N（支柱が飛び出す音）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.69,0:18:40.66,phi main,,0,0,0,,Hearts 10!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.11,0:18:48.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出口を作った。　もう　カイトの勝ちだ。\Nでも…。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.18,0:18:44.73,phi main,,0,0,0,,He made an exit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.73,0:18:46.43,phi main,,0,0,0,,Kaito won!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.43,0:18:47.19,phi main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.85,0:18:53.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,スペードの３４。\N（支柱が飛び出す音）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.99,0:18:50.57,phi main,,0,0,0,,Spades 34!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.76,0:18:58.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハートの１。\N（支柱が飛び出す音）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.82,0:18:55.29,phi main,,0,0,0,,Hearts 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.71,0:19:02.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだ？\N心の声\Nカイトの狙いが読めねえ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.74,0:19:02.32,phi main,,0,0,0,,What? I can't see what he's aiming for.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.20,0:19:07.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ギャモン）スペードの３５！\N一体　何をするつもり？　大門カイト。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:03.48,phi main,,0,0,0,,Spades 35!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.48,0:19:05.83,phi main,,0,0,0,,What is he trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.83,0:19:06.87,phi main,,0,0,0,,Daimon Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.72,0:19:09.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダイヤの５９。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.86,0:19:09.08,phi main,,0,0,0,,Diamonds 59!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.08,0:19:14.21,phi main,,0,0,0,,He doesn't have the Armband of Orpheus on, but his thinking is still at high speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.71,0:19:14.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オルペウスの腕輪が外れているのに\N思考速度は上がったままだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.48,0:19:18.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,超加速させながら\N理性を保ってる。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.61,0:19:17.60,phi main,,0,0,0,,He's staying rational while speeding up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.42,0:19:23.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ギャモン君には\Nもうスペードの１５を動かして→
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.75,0:19:26.18,phi main,,0,0,0,,Gammon has no choice but to move spades 15 and hit Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:26.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイト君にぶつける以外に手はない。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.97,0:19:32.42,phi main,,0,0,0,,But if he does that, he'll end up blocking his own way to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.97,0:19:31.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし　そんなことをすれば\Nギャモン君は　自分が地上に出る道を→
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.18,0:19:34.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,閉ざすことに…。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.48,0:19:39.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,スペードの１５！\N（支柱が飛び出す音）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.57,0:19:36.61,phi main,,0,0,0,,Spades 15!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.09,0:19:42.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダイヤの９９。\N（支柱が飛び出す音）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.30,0:19:40.74,phi main,,0,0,0,,Diamonds 99!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:44.27,phi main,,0,0,0,,Kaito won!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.86,0:19:45.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイトの勝ちだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.40,0:20:46.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ギャモン！\Nギャモン君！\Nギャモン！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.51,0:20:43.51,phi main,,0,0,0,,Gammon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.89,0:20:44.76,phi main,,0,0,0,,Gammon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.26,0:20:49.53,phi main,,0,0,0,,Shit! How did he do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.32,0:20:49.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,心の声\Nくそっ！　なんてこった。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.27,0:20:52.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺のパズルに　こんな隙が\N心の声\Nあったとはな…。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.53,0:20:52.27,phi main,,0,0,0,,He realized my puzzle had a fault like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.63,0:20:55.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,心の声\N最後に　支柱が　同時に\N飛び出すようにしたものの→
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.80,0:20:56.10,phi main,,0,0,0,,When the beams are all extending at the same time in the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.91,0:20:59.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それでは　互いの角が\N心の声\Nぶつかって止まってしまう。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.10,0:20:58.92,phi main,,0,0,0,,their corners clash and they stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.53,0:21:04.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイトのやつ　四隅は\N心の声\N安全だってことを見抜いて…。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.76,0:21:03.78,phi main,,0,0,0,,Kaito knew that the corners were safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.29,0:21:06.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無意味に見えた支柱の動きは→
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.44,0:21:10.66,phi main,,0,0,0,,He used those pointless moves to make Gammon run to that point.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.94,0:21:11.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ギャモン君を　あの空間に逃すための\N階段だったんだね…。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.28,0:21:17.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,けっ。　シャレ乙なマネしやがる。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.42,0:21:17.33,phi main,,0,0,0,,That fucker used my puzzle to show off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.55,0:21:21.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それでこそ　倒し甲斐が\Nあるってもんだぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.73,0:21:20.49,phi main,,0,0,0,,All the more reason to try and defeat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.89,0:21:29.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バッカみたい。\N何が　狙いは　神のパズルよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.05,0:21:30.00,phi main,,0,0,0,,So stupid! "Aiming for the Divine Puzzle" my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.86,0:21:34.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やってらんないわ。　あんたたちで\N好きに仲よくやってなさいよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.00,0:21:33.94,phi main,,0,0,0,,I can't take this. You can just do your "best friends forever" thing on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.65,0:21:37.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイト！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.86,0:21:35.91,phi main,,0,0,0,,Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.73,0:21:41.19,phi main,,0,0,0,,I believed in you! I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.86,0:21:41.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪（キュービック）僕は信じてたよ！\N大好き～！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.38,0:21:49.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,腕輪を　捨てた…。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.53,0:21:48.66,phi main,,0,0,0,,You threw the Armband away...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.55,0:21:53.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜだ？\Nなぜ　僕の隣に来ないんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.77,0:21:53.69,phi main,,0,0,0,,Why? Why won't you come to my side?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.35,0:21:56.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ルーク様。\Nイヤだ…　イヤだぁ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.69,0:21:54.99,phi main,,0,0,0,,Sir Rook...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.99,0:22:00.06,phi main,,0,0,0,,No... No... No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.79,0:22:00.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ！\Nイヤだ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.03,0:22:04.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（３人）うっ。\N僕のカイト　僕のカイト～！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.46,0:22:04.26,phi main,,0,0,0,,Kaito is mine! Kaito is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.57,0:22:07.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,落ち着いてください　ルーク様！\Nイヤだ…　イヤだぁ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.71,0:22:06.22,phi main,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Sir Rook!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.22,0:22:08.05,phi main,,0,0,0,,No... No!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.72,0:22:11.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイト…　カイトは　僕のものなんだぁ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.05,0:22:11.64,phi main,,0,0,0,,Kaito... Kaito is mine and only mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.41,0:22:17.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ。\Nカイト　カイト。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.48,0:22:17.99,phi main,,0,0,0,,Kaito... Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.80,0:22:23.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ルーク様。\N待って　カイト。　隣に…　僕の隣に！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.99,0:22:18.60,phi main,,0,0,0,,Sir Rook...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.60,0:22:20.23,phi main,,0,0,0,,Wait! Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.36,0:22:22.98,phi main,,0,0,0,,Come... to my side...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.70,0:22:22.36,phi main,,0,0,0,,Sir Rook!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.48,0:22:27.23,phi main,,0,0,0,,Kaito is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.55,0:22:28.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕のカイト～！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.12,0:22:40.46,phi ED romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}tsukue no ue de umareta sekai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.12,0:22:40.46,phi ED english,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}This world born on my table.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.46,0:22:46.05,phi ED romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}ichiban saki ni kimi ni misetakatta
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.46,0:22:46.05,phi ED english,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}I wanted you to see it first.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.05,0:22:56.47,phi ED romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}karappo no heya sotto nukedashite hashiri hajimeteta
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.05,0:22:56.47,phi ED english,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}I sneaked out of the empty room and started to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.23,0:23:01.52,phi ED romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}iki hazamasete oka wo noboru to
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.23,0:23:01.52,phi ED english,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}As I got to the top of the hill, out of breath,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.52,0:23:06.90,phi ED romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}kimi ga saki ni tsuite matteita ne
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.52,0:23:06.90,phi ED english,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}you were already there waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.78,0:23:17.33,phi ED romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}takusan no hajimete kimi to mitsuketa takaramono datta
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.78,0:23:17.33,phi ED english,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}It was the first of many treasures we would find together.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.33,0:23:22.96,phi ED romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}kanashisa de afureta toki wa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.33,0:23:22.96,phi ED english,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}When sorrow was overflowing in me,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.96,0:23:27.76,phi ED romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}nanimo iwazu ni tada soba ni ite kureta ne
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.96,0:23:27.76,phi ED english,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}you just silently stayed by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.26,0:23:32.84,phi ED romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}ima de mo wasurenai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.26,0:23:32.84,phi ED english,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}I still haven't forgotten that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.84,0:23:38.18,phi ED romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}mata aou ne yakusoku wo shiyou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.84,0:23:38.18,phi ED english,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Let's promise we'll meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.18,0:23:43.40,phi ED romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}kie wa shinai ano hi no sayonara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.18,0:23:43.40,phi ED english,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}The goodbye of that day we'll never forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.40,0:23:48.61,phi ED romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}boku no subete kimi ga kureta michi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.40,0:23:48.61,phi ED english,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}All I have I got from you,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.99,0:23:57.41,phi ED romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(0,1200)}zutto kokoro no naka hikaru yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.99,0:23:57.41,phi ED english,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(0,1200)}and it will all shine in my heart forever.
